{
  "stem": "19055.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we could feel that we were really at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our, our, our family and, and maybe his brother and family who also lived in Szeghalom, and, and my mother's uncles maybe, and some of my friends' parents.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes the high holidays-- we never went to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father spent all his day at shul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, we had to be there also with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to go out to the backyard and, and play whenever you could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I fasted until noon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my parents fasted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The high holidays [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] always filled, filled me with with mystery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It, it was a very mystic ritual to me to see those people in their, in their white, in their tennis shoes, or in their slippers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they told me that, you know, they buried the Jews also in those outfits.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a bit-- I was a bit fearful in those days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I certainly prayed strong for my family always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I, I was a believer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I still am.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Up until that point, I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I accepted without any question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I enjoyed all what came with the, the, the wonderful stories from, from the Bible, the, the company, the school, the teachers, the, the learning a new language, and the traditions, and, and everything with it, up until I encountered anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the questions came, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, you grow up in, in a, a very chauvinistic country, like little Hungary with the national anthem, the flag.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and you feel patriotic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You do feel-- I felt patriotic until, until they kept telling me that you're not Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're a Jew, even then.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
